  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/843440/extras/594b2d12bda8e9f05d8a0e37d0d71566.poster.avif?t=1745903582\" width=616 height=32 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/843440/extras/594b2d12bda8e9f05d8a0e37d0d71566.webm?t=1745903582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/843440/extras/594b2d12bda8e9f05d8a0e37d0d71566.mp4?t=1745903582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Pivot your character within the screen’s borders, narrowly dodging obstacles, collecting points, and smashing power-ups. Survive as long as possible in this fast-paced, minimalist arcade experience, the second game in my three-part series.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/843440/extras/634d535499653e3d5322cee8e6a607a1.poster.avif?t=1745903582\" width=616 height=32 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/843440/extras/634d535499653e3d5322cee8e6a607a1.webm?t=1745903582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/843440/extras/634d535499653e3d5322cee8e6a607a1.mp4?t=1745903582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press the <strong>pivot button</strong> to start spinning in the opposite direction. <strong>Simple one-button controls</strong> make it easy to pick up but hard to master. Play with a <strong>gamepad, keyboard, or mouse</strong> for seamless input.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/843440/extras/e3882b7a9f05f8f03f080023863e5dbc.poster.avif?t=1745903582\" width=616 height=32 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/843440/extras/e3882b7a9f05f8f03f080023863e5dbc.webm?t=1745903582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/843440/extras/e3882b7a9f05f8f03f080023863e5dbc.mp4?t=1745903582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Easy to learn, hard to master</strong> – Simple controls, deep challenge</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless score-chasing action</strong> – The game speeds up over time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlockable skins</strong> – Includes characters from other Adamvision Studios games</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>‘Close Call’ system</strong> – Earn bonus points for near misses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Leaderboards & Steam Achievements</strong> – Compete for the top score globally</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Cloud support</strong> – Sync progress across devices</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Trading Cards</strong> – Includes profile wallpapers & emoticons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Perfect for quick sessions</strong> – Great for playing while waiting in queue</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simple yet unique sound design</strong> – Audio SFX created using my own voice + royalty-free sounds</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/843440/extras/50708eef5b94a8f697a3c63bd3a22328.poster.avif?t=1745903582\" width=616 height=32 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/843440/extras/50708eef5b94a8f697a3c63bd3a22328.webm?t=1745903582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/843440/extras/50708eef5b94a8f697a3c63bd3a22328.mp4?t=1745903582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pivot XL is a <strong>small, replayable arcade score-chaser</strong> designed for fast, high-intensity gameplay. As the second game in my minimalist arcade series, it builds on my original mobile game <strong>‘Pivot’</strong> with refined mechanics and PC-optimized features.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I love crafting <strong>simple, polished arcade games</strong> and truly value player feedback. If you find a bug, have suggestions, or just want to say hello, reach out via <strong>Discord</strong> or my <strong>website</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thanks for playing!<br><strong>Adam Nickerson - Adamvision Studios</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SOUNDTRACK</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"All Night Long\"</i> by <strong>meHiLove</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/843440/extras/594b2d12bda8e9f05d8a0e37d0d71566.poster.avif?t=1745903582\" width=616 height=32 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/843440/extras/594b2d12bda8e9f05d8a0e37d0d71566.webm?t=1745903582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/843440/extras/594b2d12bda8e9f05d8a0e37d0d71566.mp4?t=1745903582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Pivot your character within the screen’s borders, narrowly dodging obstacles, collecting points, and smashing power-ups. Survive as long as possible in this fast-paced, minimalist arcade experience, the second game in my three-part series.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/843440/extras/634d535499653e3d5322cee8e6a607a1.poster.avif?t=1745903582\" width=616 height=32 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/843440/extras/634d535499653e3d5322cee8e6a607a1.webm?t=1745903582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/843440/extras/634d535499653e3d5322cee8e6a607a1.mp4?t=1745903582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press the <strong>pivot button</strong> to start spinning in the opposite direction. <strong>Simple one-button controls</strong> make it easy to pick up but hard to master. Play with a <strong>gamepad, keyboard, or mouse</strong> for seamless input.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/843440/extras/e3882b7a9f05f8f03f080023863e5dbc.poster.avif?t=1745903582\" width=616 height=32 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/843440/extras/e3882b7a9f05f8f03f080023863e5dbc.webm?t=1745903582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/843440/extras/e3882b7a9f05f8f03f080023863e5dbc.mp4?t=1745903582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Easy to learn, hard to master</strong> – Simple controls, deep challenge</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless score-chasing action</strong> – The game speeds up over time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlockable skins</strong> – Includes characters from other Adamvision Studios games</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>‘Close Call’ system</strong> – Earn bonus points for near misses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Leaderboards & Steam Achievements</strong> – Compete for the top score globally</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Cloud support</strong> – Sync progress across devices</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Trading Cards</strong> – Includes profile wallpapers & emoticons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Perfect for quick sessions</strong> – Great for playing while waiting in queue</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simple yet unique sound design</strong> – Audio SFX created using my own voice + royalty-free sounds</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/843440/extras/50708eef5b94a8f697a3c63bd3a22328.poster.avif?t=1745903582\" width=616 height=32 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/843440/extras/50708eef5b94a8f697a3c63bd3a22328.webm?t=1745903582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/843440/extras/50708eef5b94a8f697a3c63bd3a22328.mp4?t=1745903582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pivot XL is a <strong>small, replayable arcade score-chaser</strong> designed for fast, high-intensity gameplay. As the second game in my minimalist arcade series, it builds on my original mobile game <strong>‘Pivot’</strong> with refined mechanics and PC-optimized features.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I love crafting <strong>simple, polished arcade games</strong> and truly value player feedback. If you find a bug, have suggestions, or just want to say hello, reach out via <strong>Discord</strong> or my <strong>website</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thanks for playing!<br><strong>Adam Nickerson - Adamvision Studios</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SOUNDTRACK</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"All Night Long\"</i> by <strong>meHiLove</strong></p>",
